<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">The alliance forms stands along washes disturbed by fluvial processes. Most upland stands are sparse and rocky; however, fire can affect them in years when introduced or native annuals form dense enough flashy fuels. The species sprouts following fire, as it does sprout after mechanical disturbance (Keeler-Wolf et al. 1998b). Fire kills related species of <i>Agave </i>(Uchytil 1990b).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
			<td>Truncated long
				
