    <div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
        <h4 class="header">Regional Status</h4>
        

        <ul class="text">
        
            <li><b>Colorado Desert</b> (322Cb). Conspicuous stands exist in Anza-Borrego Desert State Park (Keeler-Wolf et al. 1998b).</li>
        
            <li><b>Southern California Mountains and Valleys</b> (M262Bp). Stands exist near Anza-Borrego Desert State Park (Keeler-Wolf et al. 1998b) and above Palm Springs in bottomland settings; upland stands occur to around 1000 m.</li>
        
        </ul>
    </div>


    
	
<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Management Considerations</h4>
	<div class="text"> Responses to fire and other disturbances are relatively unknown. </div>
</div>

    

    

    <div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
